quran[10{c,v,t}:
24,44,raat aur din ka ulat phair wohi kar raha hai iss mein aik sabaq hai aankhon walon ke liye
24,45,"aur Allah ne har jandaar aik terhan ke pani se peda kya, koi pait ke bil chal raha hai to koi do tangon par aur koi chaar tangon par jo kuch woh chahta hai peda karta hai, woh har cheez par Qadir hai"
24,46,"hum ne saaf saaf haqeeqat bitanay wali ayaat nazil kar di hain, agay Siraat mustaqeem ki taraf hadaayat Allah hi jisay chahta hai deta hai"
24,47,"yeh log kehte hain ke hum imaan laaye Allah aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam par aur hum ne itaat qubool ki, magar is ke baad un mein se aik giroh ( itaat se ) mun mourr jata hai aisay log hargiz momin nahi hain"
24,48,"jab un ko bulaya jata hai Allah aur rasool ki taraf, taakay rasool un ke aapas ke muqadmay ka faisla kere to un mein se aik fareeq katra jata hai"
24,49,Albata agar haq un ki muwafiqat mein ho to rasool ke paas barray itaat kish ban kar aa jatay hain
24,50,kya un ke dilon ko ( munafqat ka ) rog laga howa hai? ya yeh shak mein parre hue hain? ya un ko yeh khauf hai ke Allah aur is ka rasool un par zulm kere ga? asal baat yeh hai ke zalim to yeh log khud hain
24,51,imaan laane walon ka kaam to yeh hai ke jab woh Allah aur rasool ki taraf bulaa ye jayen taakay rasool un ke muqadmay ka faisla kere to woh kahin ke hum ne suna aur itaat ki aisay hi log Falah panay walay hain
24,52,aur kamyaab wohi hain jo Allah aur rasool ki farmaa bardari karen aur Allah se dareen aur is ki nafarmani se bachchen
24,53,"yeh ( munafiq ) Allah ke naam se kari kari kasmain kha kar kehte hain ke"" aap hukum den to hum gharon se nikal kharray hon"" inn se kaho"" kasmain nah khao, tumhari itaat ka haal maloom hai, tumahray krtoton se Allah be khabar nahi hai """
